title: 217: Peterson Trade, Buying Stock in College Programs
itunes:title: 217: Peterson Trade, Buying Stock in College Programs
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks react to the Cardinals acquiring Adrian Peterson from the Saints (2:20). The guys also dive into Mitchell Trubisky's first career start (5:30). DJ and Bucky wrap the show by picking which five schools they would take official visits to (13:55) before they buy future stock in big-time programs around the country (18:20).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
